title: MisterMusic Show 302 indie,alternative,rock Radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 302  (2 hours) 192kbps MP3 Stereo-


It's another episode of the MisterMusic Show, with new tunes by James, Echo & The Bunnymen,Gardens & Villa, and another new one from Fujiya & Miyagi.

Also, we revisit May 1991 for a big hit that spent 2 weeks at number 1 on the US modern rock chart.
It's a blend of new indie and alternative music mixed with classic hits from over 5 decades of rock.


The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
